âš ï¸ ETHICAL CONSIDERATIONS
================================================================================
âŒ BIASES TO WATCH FOR:
   - Socioeconomic bias (family income affects study hours)
   - Gender bias (different patterns by gender)
   - Cultural bias (language barriers for international students)
   - Previous failure bias (past failures don't guarantee future failure)

âœ“ SOLUTIONS:
   - Diverse training data
   - Regular audit for fairness
   - Explainable predictions
   - Human oversight (AI assists, not replaces decisions)

